node.text:
Our pre-launch promo has ended! A HUGE thank you to all our kind supporters, giving us power and strength to move forward during these tough times. 🙏
Your support means a great deal to us in keeping our dreams and passion alive. Be part of our journey as we continue to pursue our dreams! 💪💪
•
𝟏𝟖𝟓𝟓 @ 𝐇𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐢𝐬 𝐨𝐟𝐟𝐢𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲 𝐎𝐏𝐄𝐍! 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤 𝐢𝐧 𝐛𝐢𝐨.⁠ We are more than ready to share our love for food - 𝙨𝙚𝙣𝙙 𝙞𝙣 𝙮𝙤𝙪𝙧 𝙤𝙧𝙙𝙚𝙧𝙨!
[Place your orders] Whatsapp +65 9835 9972⁠
[Open daily] 10.30am-8.00pm⁠

Don’t forget to tag us @1855fnb with your #diningathome pics! ❤️
•
